OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781470068
OL,3,CNew cancer building to offer 700 extra
OL,4,Cradiotherapy treatments each year
OL,6,FA new cancer centre has opened at
OL,7,FDerriford Hospital which will offer
OL,8,F700 extra treatments of radiotherapy
OL,9,Feach year.
OL,11,FThe #18.5million building includes
OL,12,Fstate-of-the-art equipment expected to
OL,13,Fimprove the precision and efficiency
OL,14,Fof treatment, and reduce treatment
OL,15,Ftimes.
OL,17,FChristopher Delridge, a Cornish
OL,18,Ffarmer, is halfway through his
OL,19,Fradiotherapy for prostate cancer. He's
OL,20,Fthe first patient to use the new
OL,21,Fequipment.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781470068
OL,3,CNew cancer building to offer 700 extra
OL,4,Cradiotherapy treatments each year
OL,6,FHe said: "It's exciting for people
OL,7,Flike myself who have a cancer
OL,8,Fdiagnosis that the hospital now has
OL,9,Fbetter improved facilities and more
OL,10,Fcapacity, so it's obviously going to
OL,11,Fbe very helpful for people who have a
OL,12,Fcancer journey ahead of them.
OL,14,F"This is my 10th treatment today of
OL,15,F20. The whole experience here at the
OL,16,Foncology unit has been brilliant,
OL,17,Fstaff are so welcoming and friendly
OL,18,Fwith a bit of humour as well.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781470068
OL,3,CNew cancer building to offer 700 extra
OL,4,Cradiotherapy treatments each year
OL,6,F"It's made this rather unpleasant
OL,7,Fprocess really very human and very
OL,8,Fnice."
OL,10,FChris Bowen, the radiotherapy services
OL,11,Flead at University Hospitals Plymouth
OL,12,FNHS Trust (UHP), said the new building
OL,13,Fhad been years in the making.
OL,15,FHe said: "For a number of years the
OL,16,FRadiotherapy department has had three
OL,17,FLINAC machines, all of which are older
OL,18,Fthan we would like.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781470068
OL,3,CNew cancer building to offer 700 extra
OL,4,Cradiotherapy treatments each year
OL,6,F"Now, with the construction of a new
OL,7,Fradiotherapy decant bunker, we not
OL,8,Fonly have the room for a brand-new,
OL,9,Fadvanced treatment machine, but we can
OL,10,Falso begin to replace our older
OL,11,Fmachines without affecting the service
OL,12,Fwe deliver.
OL,14,F"As a relatively small department we
OL,15,Fpunch well above our weight in terms
OL,16,Fof the range of services we are able
OL,17,Fto provide for our patients and are
OL,18,Falways looking for opportunities to
OL,19,Fimprove and innovate.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781470068
OL,3,CNew cancer building to offer 700 extra
OL,4,Cradiotherapy treatments each year
OL,6,F"With the completion of this new
OL,7,Fextension and the new opportunities
OL,8,Fthe new technology can provide, we are
OL,9,Freally excited that now we can further
OL,10,Fdevelop the service, advance our
OL,11,Ftechniques and provide our patients
OL,12,Fwith greater access to the latest
OL,13,Ftreatment regimes."
OL,15,FThe facility has been opened in memory
OL,16,Fof BBC Radio Devon presenter and
OL,17,FPlymouth Argyle commentator, Gordon
OL,18,FSparks who was a former and "fondly-
OL,19,Fremembered" patient of the
OL,20,Fradiotherapy team.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781470068
OL,3,CNew cancer building to offer 700 extra
OL,4,Cradiotherapy treatments each year
OL,6,FHeather Sparks, Gordon's wife, said:
OL,7,F"Gordon was always passionate about
OL,8,FDerriford Hospital, the staff and the
OL,9,Fservice it provided.
OL,11,F"He liked to offer support when he
OL,12,Fcould and when he needed treatment
OL,13,Fhimself he was cared for excellently.
OL,15,F"I feel honoured to have been asked to
OL,16,Fopen the new Plymouth Oncology Centre
OL,17,Fextension in Gordon's memory. It is a
OL,18,Fwonderful tribute to him and the whole
OL,19,Ffamily are incredibly touched by this
OL,20,Fdedication."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
